de.uniulm.omi.cloudiator.sword.api.service

Interface DiscoveryService<H extends HardwareFlavor,I extends Image,L extends Location,V extends VirtualMachine>

  • Type Parameters:
    H - the type of the HardwareFlavor
    I - the type of the Image
    L - the type of the Location
    V - the type of the VirtualMachine
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseDiscoveryService

    public interface DiscoveryService<H extends HardwareFlavor,I extends Image,L extends Location,V extends VirtualMachine>
    Provides methods to either directly fetch resources (HardwareFlavor, Image, Location and Virtual Machine) stored at the cloud provider or to fetch all resources of a specific type.
